cdata.name: Digix Gold token
cdata.desc: Digix is an asset tokenization platformthat puts gold assetownershipon the blockchain, making digital gold transferrable. Digix' ecosystem is powered by two native tokens: DGX and DGD.DGX is an ERC20 security token which democratizes access to gold. DGXrepresents physical gold where 1 DGX represents 1 gram of gold.The DGD token gives users the right to profits in the trading of DGX tokens which own the right to gold stored in a vault in Singapore. So if people trade 20 gold bars per day - theDGD token holders will have the profits of the commission from those trades distributed equally amongst themselves.
